        <h2 class="h2">Our Story</h2>
        <h3 class="h3">The best night at Banditos</h3>
        <p>
            Liz and Michael met in the summer of 2012 during college.
            Michael crashed a birthday party for Liz's good friend Cooper.
            Michael liked the looks of Liz, and he strategically seated himself across from Liz during dinner.
            He spent the whole evening chatting her up and boasting about
            his cooking skills.
        </p>
        <p>
            After the party, Liz went home to Wilmington,
            and they texted each other all summer. Liz wasn’t sold on
            Michael quite yet, but he had promised to cook her a meal
            when she returned to Chapel Hill.
        </p>
