        <h3 class="h3">Our senior year</h3>
        <p>
            In the fall of 2012, both Michael and Liz moved back to Chapel
            Hill for their final year at UNC Chapel Hill. Michael coaxed
            Liz on a date with lamb risotto. She warmed up to Michael, and they
            spent next few months bonding over TV shows, UNC basketball, food, and music.
        </p>
        <p>
            Both Liz and Michael were music minors, and Liz was thrilled
            to learn that Michael knew all the words to Coney Island Baby
            (a popular song at Liz’s family reunion). Michael was excited
            to find someone to test out his recipes and attend his
            Men’s Glee concerts.
        </p>
