        <h3 class="h3">She said yes</h3>
        <p>
            After graduation in summer of 2013, Michael took a job with IBM.
            Liz only applied for jobs in the Raleigh/Durham/Chapel Hill area, because she knew she didn’t
            want to move far from Michael. She was lucky to find a job in
            Mebane, 20 miles west of Chapel Hill. Michael’s job at IBM
            was 20 miles east of Chapel Hill. They both decided to stay
            put in the town of their alma mater where they saw each other
            every evening.
        </p>
